data.description: This spacious 3 bed 2 bath home on 10 acres is the perfect place to call your own. With plenty of room to spread out and relax, you'll never feel cramped here. The large living room is perfect for entertaining guests, and the kitchen is bright and airy with wonderful large windows. The master bedroom has its own private bathroom and large closet!The property also includes a detached garage, a shed, and 10 acres of land! The garage is perfect for storing your vehicles and tools, and the shed can be used for storage or for hobbies. The land is perfect for gardening, raising livestock, or just enjoying the peace and quiet of the countryside.The home is located just under 20 minutes from the Holiday gas station, so you're never far from civilization.  Another great perk of this home is that it has a double meter on the heat. This means that you can get a significant discount on your heating bill by utilizing MWEC. The membership will transfer to the new owner, so you don't have to worry about anything.The home also has a new F-Wave roof that was installed in 2022. This roof is made of durable materials that will protect your home from the elements for years to come.
